 The first phase of Disney 's Polynesian Villas & Bungalows has been unveiled , revealing opulent overwater villas available from $ 2,000 a night - rising to $ 4,500 at peak times .
The overwater suites are a first of their kind for Disney , boasting two bedrooms , two bathrooms and a private plunge pool .
The villas feel more like Bora Bora than Florida .